Dialogue: 0,0:00:-12.-27,0:00:-10.-26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-10.-24,0:00:-08.-36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-08.-34,0:00:-06.-05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-03,0:00:-02.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-02.-16,0:00:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anyone we can't\Nabandon, it's Bellemere!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Why did this have to happen?!\NDon't act hasty, Bellemere!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious! Nothing's quite like\Nmy special tangerine sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten more minutes for\Nthe duck in the oven.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.42,0:01:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got the side of vegetables...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the stew is boiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now just some fried rice omelets,\Nand everything's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.53,0:02:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be a big blow\Nto our family budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are they back?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Survive! Mother Bellemere\Nand Nami's Bond!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.17,0:02:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's open! Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad. I'm a former marine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brings Grand Line pirates\Nall the way out to Cocoyashi Village?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Powerless! Powerless!\NPowerless! Powerless! Powerless!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How powerless your\Ninferior species is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's escape with her\Nout the back door!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.14,0:03:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the pirates might already be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:03:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.91,0:04:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Doctor!\N--You mustn't return home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wha...?\N--Move! We have to save Bellemere-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nojiko! Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen closely, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This may not be the best situation to--\N no, because of the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must tell you a somewhat cruel story!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good!\NThese guys are real monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nojiko! Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste your life for some\Npathetic sense of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some battles aren't worth fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some issues can be solved with money!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, marine girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100,000 per adult. 50,000 per kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can pay for your\Nwhole family, I'll let you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be thankful I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My whole family?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's 200,000 total.\NHow much do you own, all together?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Including what I've squirreled\Naway... a little over 100,000...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! There's a meal\Nfor three people in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? A family of three, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I almost forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.17,0:05:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She invited me and my\Nfriend to dinner tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Bellemere.\NHurry and pay your amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our delicious food's going to get cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you have 100,000.\NThank goodness you have enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone in the village is spared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the village register has no record\Nof her getting married or giving birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's single.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:06:01.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Single" "No Family"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no proof that you two\Nand Bellemere are family!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this island before\Nthey take notice of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.07,0:06:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Escape across the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other way for\Nall three of you to survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel it's reckless to send you two\Nout to sea at such a young age!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a chance\Nsomething bad could happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But at least you'll have...\N--No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to leave?\NThey're the ones who came here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... want to live in this village...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because we're poor
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I can't be\NBellemere-san's kid anymore?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.81,0:06:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness. Now they won't kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Alright, we'll leave the village!\N--Nojiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:07:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! Because that means\NBellemere-san gets to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said I paid for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That 100,000's for my two daughters.\NI don't got enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bellemere! What are you...\N--I'm sorry, Gen-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't say\NI don't have a family...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even... if it costs me my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, maybe we're\Nnot related by blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but we're a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be their parent,\Neven if it's only in name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're... my kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bellemere-san!\N--Wait, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish someone richer\Nhad adopted me instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a lie! I was lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted... to buy you lots\Nmore books and clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was never able to do\Nanything mother-like for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need anything!\NJust don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with us forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to see\Nthe world map I draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Your map...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make your dream... come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These're your girls, I take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me you won't\Nlay a hand on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! As long as\Nyou die like a good girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.56,0:09:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now they're thirsty for blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kill 'em.\NJust handle 'em as you see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing for our\Nfirst example to the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die with your pathetic love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nojiko! Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just never learn, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! I'll pay later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--With my body!\N--You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made another boy cry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He made me mad!\N--Blehhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Kids will be kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said your tangerines\Nsuck, Bellemere-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Say what?!\N--Bellemere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give in to anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even girls need to be strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if\Npeople don't praise you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't have hate for this\Nera you were born in...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never forget the strength to\Nbe able to smile at any time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under my rule,\Nanyone without money dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand, you inferior species?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:10:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A sea chart?\N--No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I drew that! It's important\Nto me! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You drew it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Give it back!\N--Nami! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? This is quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.78,0:11:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's an invaluable asset!\NBring her with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Right!\N--No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! Let go! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let Nami go! Let go!\N--Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got your money!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised not\Nto lay a hand on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I ain't gonna hurt her.\NI'm just gonna borrow her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-san! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your hands off the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-san! Gen-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save you, Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.99,0:12:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's okay!\NYou don't need to save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This is getting tedious.\N--I'll... save...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, no more dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the village's\Nships have been sunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our idea of trying to let\NNojiko and Nami escape to sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was too optimistic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I feared,\Nthe navy won't listen to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This island will be under his control.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She fully knew how they work,\Nfrom her experience as a marine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:13:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She knew not a single\Nperson could ever escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They took Nami with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.06,0:13:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... am I supposed to\Ndo now... Bellemere-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've found out where\Nthe Arlong Pirates are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they intend to\Nsettle down on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.47,0:13:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we fight now and die defiantly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do we place our hope in waiting\Nfor help from the government,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while living under the fear\Nof being killed at any time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one or the other!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only Navy Headquarters\Nstands a chance against them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But HQ has its hands full\Nin the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our hopes of them coming all the\Nway out here are as good as zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.66,0:13:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't let Nami go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too! I doubt I can live my life\Nknowing I abandoned a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:13:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all family here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it means I die killing them,\NI'm gonna save Nacchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere gave her\Nlife up to protect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight 'em again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll blame us all anyway\Nif just one of us fights!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you survive, lots\Nof fun things will happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.74,0:14:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami!\N--Nacchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? Are you hurt?\NDid they do anything to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami?\N--I'm... joining...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm joining... the Arlong Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to join the Arlong Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to be a surveyor and draw sea charts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Nami?\NAre you in your right mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they do something\Nhorrible to you? Did they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--They threatened you, didn't they?!\N--No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Say it!\N--Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.92,0:15:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's an Arlong tattoo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this...\NThey gave me all this money...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they say they'll\Nbuy me anything I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable! Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joining pirates is\Nabsolutely unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And them, of all people!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even know what\Nkind of people they are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.96,0:15:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm gonna get killed living\Na proper life like Bellemere-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I don't wanna live properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san was killed because of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How can you just...\N--That's enough, Nojiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never step foot into this village again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could she be so foolish?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she not see\NBellemere as her parent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not true...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:17:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami loved Bellemere-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san said that if we survive,\Nfun things will happen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of fun things...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.41,0:17:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After Arlong dragged me off,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.15,0:17:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,five navy ships came to capture him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they were all sunk easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think the government will\Nsend any more help to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what made me realize\NI have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.43,0:17:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made an agreement with Arlong
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to buy Cocoyashi Village from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To buy the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For 100 million Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.44,0:17:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I buy the village, we can be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one else will have to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, I have to join his\Ngroup and draw sea charts...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, 100 million Berries?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure you can earn that\Nmuch working your entire life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:18:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will earn it!\NNo matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's working their\Nhardest to pay the tribute money,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so my only choice is to do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if I ask for help from\Nanyone, more people will get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It'll hurt, you know...\N--Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Staying with the people who\Nkilled Bellemere-san'll hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.44,0:18:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine. I'll put on a big smile,\Neven when I see his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided not to cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to fight on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how painful of\Na choice it was for Nami
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to decide to fight and survive on\Nher own, at the mere age of 10?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the only deal that\Ncould save the village, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make whoever makes\Nmy beloved Nami-san suffer--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why, Big Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you! I came here\Nto tell you to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.50,0:19:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you make a big fuss\Nabout her being your friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the pirates'll grow suspicious of Nami
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.80,0:19:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and her eight years of fighting\Nwill be all for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make her suffer\Nany more than she has.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has to fight alone,\Nso the most painful thing for her
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is having people who\Ncall her their friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Get back here! Damn brat!\N--How dare you steal our treasure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:20:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stealing from pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm using the huge number of\Npirates in this era to my advantage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like, "You get what you deserve!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're covered in cuts, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I sorta screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But look at this! One million Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.89,0:20:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that! You need\Nmedical treatment, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine! It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will ever find it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gather money little by little,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it'll be 100 million\Nwhen I'm grown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a long ways to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100 million Berries...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's taken a long time,\Nbut just seven million left...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can earn that much now in one try!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one more journey,\Nand it'll all be over...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in Cocoyashi Village\Nand I will be free of Arlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:20:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I think I can finally\Nsmile from the bottom of my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does the navy want with Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You simply need to lead the way quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does that old guy have\Na pinwheel on his head?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.08,0:21:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll get started on\Nmy final act of plundering!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.49,0:22:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The navy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why is Gen-san with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the girl thief known as Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.34,0:22:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our information has it you've hidden\Ntreasure you stole from pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.67,0:22:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in this tangerine orchard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.54,0:22:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were pirates, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.71,0:22:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intentions\Nof condemning you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.38,0:22:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, stealing is stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.55,0:22:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, as of this moment,\Nall of the property you've stolen
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.59,0:22:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,now belongs to the government!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now give us all of your stolen goods!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.63,0:22:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're confiscating it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:23:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.41,0:23:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Now we know\Nall about this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.48,0:23:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry and meet up with Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.74,0:24:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.01,0:24:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What're you doing?\N--Appreciating happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.98,0:24:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can stop Nami-san's suffering\Nwith my own two hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.79,0:24:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nami! What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.02,0:24:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still here?!\NJust leave the island already!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.99,0:24:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.22,0:24:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy Rises!\NResult of the Broken Promise!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.19,0:24:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
